moji\" />，就係因為唔夠人流，做唔到物競天擇<br />\n<br />\n要分清楚，根本時事台同政事配台既客源，本身就overlap得好緊要，根本就大部分同一堆人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e7d1a1c106d95c681a5a120f2259384588d210","tid":31954,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家高登lihkg都係一樣，兩個登一拆開，兩邊d post質素都差左好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過高登lihkg呢d就無可避免，但拆做兩個台，係好撚on9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\non9得過班五毛煩膠日日推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你開個post有料到既自然會長期第一頁<br />\n五先煩膠你唔理佢自然收皮，佢有人理即係仲有價值，影響到你燥底亦都表示佢有價值"},{"pid":"f1da43c21e219099b69ce2d5adce19f21ea94f66","tid":31954,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:32:56.000Z","msg":"你地熱普城人強馬壯緊係想拉埋想睇其他新聞post既巴打睇你地威同屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本民青眾人社泛既支持者好無癮囉講句野都要比你地屌"},{"pid":"ae4676e70969934280fa9b646474a51d35ec04e3","tid":31954,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地熱普城人強馬壯緊係想拉埋想睇其他新聞post既巴打睇你地威同屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本民青眾人社泛既支持者好無癮囉講句野都要比你地屌</blockquote><br />\n你有道理咪屌番人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網都要縮沙淆底呀？<br />\n大家上論壇就係要睇你地互屌，最好係有論據咁互屌<br />\n<br />\n上網都要玩小圈子搏認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"f6624bb2c0830d3eb613ef133cdf8d10e2a089b2","tid":31954,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家高登lihkg都係一樣，兩個登一拆開，兩邊d post質素都差左好撚多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"